description: Try our easy to follow Stir-Fried Beef & Quinoa recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Stir-Fried Beef & Quinoa Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the remaining oil in the wok and cook beans, capsicum and onion for 2 minutes. Add beef, stir-fry sauce and rice blend. Toss well to combine and cook for 2 minutes to heat through.
